data.description:
Immaculately presented, this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, boasting a den and sunroom patio, resides within the tranquil confines of Boynton Beach's esteemed Country Fair neighborhood. Meticulously remodeled, the residence exudes an aura of contemporary elegance, offering a seamless fusion of sophisticated design and modern functionality.Upon entry, guests are greeted by an inviting open floor plan, accentuated by an abundance of natural light and breathtaking views of the adjacent lake. The newly renovated kitchen stands as a focal point, adorned with pristine white cabinets and luxurious quartz countertops & moveable Island creating a culinary oasis Sky light & high hats for both casual dining and formal entertaining. home features split bedrooms, providing an oasis of privacy within the spacious primary bedroom, complete with an en-suite bathroom boasting a new double sink vanity and countertops & Guest Bathroom Further enhancing the allure, new laminated   vinyl flooring (waterproof) graces the interior, complemented by fresh paint throughout, evoking a sense of rejuvenation and refinement.

Noteworthy amenities include a newer A/C unit, ensuring optimal comfort and efficiency year-round. Additionally, storm shutters offer peace of mind during inclement weather, while a storage shed provides practical convenience for organized living.

Nestled within the heart of Boynton Beach, the Country Fair community epitomizes convenience and accessibility, situated mere minutes from a myriad of fine dining establishments, premier shopping destinations, reputable schools, verdant golf courses, and public parks. With swift access to major thoroughfares such as the Florida Turnpike and Interstate 95, as well as the pristine beaches just a short drive away, residents are afforded unparalleled convenience and lifestyle opportunities.

Moreover, the neighborhood's proximity to a range of amenities including schools, golf courses, local businesses, and healthcare facilities further enhances its desirability. Notably, the imminent arrival of a signature LA Fitness center and a neighboring shopping mall, promising to feature esteemed retailers such as Sprouts, Wawa, and Aspen Dental, underscores the community's commitment to enriching the resident experience. Also, Whole Foods Is Coming on Hagen Ranch,

In summary, this captivating residence within the esteemed Country Fair enclave presents an unparalleled opportunity to indulge in the epitome of modern luxury living amidst the serene beauty of Boynton Beach's scenic landscape.
